#Space

  1. Center and scale by week
  2. Plot all midday grand slopes
wc_wk_centered_df <- wc_qudo_df %>% 
  filter(time == "md") %>% 
  group_by(week) %>% 
  mutate(lwc_scaled = scale(lwc)) %>% 
  filter(lwc_scaled < 4)

space_mod <- lmer(water_potential ~ lwc_scaled + (lwc_scaled|week) + (1|tree), data = wc_wk_centered_df)
summary(space_mod)
